nodes.text: Corellian air cake was a dessert cake originally created on Corellia. Corellian air cake was made from dough and carbosyrup, with a fruit core. Corellian air cake was served aboard the luxury repulsortrain Gem of Alderaan and at the annual Vor-cal Feast held aboard the House Melantha Orbital Hunting Lodge over the planet Vycinyth.
